Furmanville Ave., north side, in 77th Street. This house does not appear in the 1929 Queens Atlas. The probable owners of this house were J. Bedell, 1852-1860, G.H. Sichman, 1873 to 1891, and J. Boening in 1891. One Zork, a florist, was the occupant in 1923.

May 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
